quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  68,1,Nun Peue meukeusud Nun bak awal ayat Tuhan Hadharat hana Neupeugah Demi na kalam ngon nyang jih surat
  68,2,Gata kon meuhat lagee jih peugah Nikmat Po gata gata kon gila
  68,3,Nyang le di gata pahla bak Allah Han peutoh-peutoh pahla keu gata
  68,4,Lom sipheuet gata pih jroh that leupah
  68,5,Dudoe pih taeu jih dum pih jieu
  68,6,Soe nyang bit rabue pungo sileupah
  68,7,Po gata keubit Neuteupue that-that Soe nyang bit sisat jalan ka salah Neuteupue that soe nyang na peutunyok Nyang ka geujak cok jalan got leupah
  68,8,Teuma awak nyan bek roh taseutot Nyang jikheun sulet dum ayat Allah
  68,9,Napsu jih gata meugot-got ngon jih Sang-sang bit di jih got-got that leupah
  68,10,Lom bek taseutot awak hina that Di jih sia-at ka jimeusumpah
  68,11,Tukang peusuna jak keunoe keudeh
  68,12,Atra jeh di jih bek sagai leupah Meunyo buet nyang got di jih kriet jih that Keubit jeuheut that jipubuet salah
  68,13,Keujam jih geuthee laen nibak nyan
  68,14,Areuta jih nyan cit le sileupah Meunan lom aneuk di jih pih le that
  68,15,‘Oh geukheun ayat jipaleng bagah Dum ayat Kamoe jikheun nyan dongeng Kra ureueng jameun bandum jipeugah
  68,16,Kamoe boh tanda ‘oh dudoe keu jih Bak beuralee jih meucap meukeubah
  68,17,Dilee awaknyan ka Kamoe ujoe Lagee meuujoe kawom nyang sudah Sinan na lampoh jih di kawom nyan Teuma watee nyan ka jimeusumpah Singoh ban beungoh tajak pot ase
  68,18,Hana jipike keu gop nyang susah Han sagai jibri keu ureueng gasien
  68,19,Meu troh treuk keunan ureueng ziarah Teungoh teungeut jih ureueng nyan teuka Nibak Po gata sideh geulangkah
  68,20,Jeut treuk lampoh nyan ka lagee arang Ka seupot itam anco dum bicah
  68,21,Jimeuhoi treuk ngon jih dum ‘oh beungoh
  68,22,Bandum tabeudoh jak keudeh bagah Meunyo meunapsu tajak pot ase Bak keubon sare laju talangkah
  68,23,Jijak treuk laju ngon jih meus‘ah-s‘ah
  68,24,Bek leumah-leumah tanyoe jak bagah Ureueng gasien bek jitamong keunoe Tanyoe uroe nyoe tajak pot buah
  68,25,Jijak treuk laju padahai di jih Ek jibri le jih peue-peue nyang mudah
  68,26,‘Oh ban jikalon lampoh lagee nyoe Jikheun bit tanyoe sisat sileupah
  68,27,Tapi di tanyoe han sapeue na le
  68,28,Ureueng got ate teuma kheun bagah Kon ka Lon peugah bak bandum gata Pakon han gata tapujoe Allah Takheun teuseubeh tapujoe Tuhan
  68,29,Jikheun treuk yoh nyan Subhanallah Keubit Po tanyoe Maha Suci that Tanyoe lalem that hanaban peugah
  68,30,Nyang ladom jikheun nyan salah gata Bandum jih teuma peusalah-salah
  68,31,Jikheun ceulaka bandum geutanyoe Sabab geutanyoe leupah that culah
  68,32,Kadang Neutem bri le Po geutanyoe c Laen Neugantoe nyang leubeh ceudah Taharap ampon bak Po geutanyoe
  68,33,Meunan keuh Kamoe azeub meubalah Azeub akhirat raya nibak nyoe Meunyo jiteupue han roe jih salah